data.description: Welcome to this stylish 3-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom bungalow that effortlessly combines classic charm with modern comforts. This bungalow is suitable for everyone, as it features high ceilings both upstairs and in the basement, creating an inviting and spacious ambiance. The original hardwood floors add a touch of timeless character, complementing the contemporary feel of the kitchen equipped with a gas stove and stainless steel appliances. With three cozy bedrooms and 1.5 updated baths, this home strikes the perfect balance between private bedrooms and shared living spaces. The property also features a convenient one-car garage. Nestled on a tree-lined street, this bungalow offers a fresh start for new owners. Don't miss the chance to own this affordably updated home – schedule a showing today!
